str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;Keep your login credentials private. You are responsible for any activity done under your account.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Content ownership and responsibility&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;You own the content you create (polls, comments, etc.), but you give VoteYour the right to display and store that content on our platform.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;You are responsible for what you post. Don&amp;rsquo;t upload anything you don&amp;rsquo;t have the right to, and don&amp;rsquo;t impersonate others.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Privacy and Data Use&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;We care about privacy. Seriously.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;We collect minimal data&amp;mdash;mainly your email (if you sign up), voting activity (stored anonymously), and basic technical information.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;We don&amp;rsquo;t sell your data, track your identity, or use third-party ads.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;Read our Privacy Policy for the full breakdown.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;\/ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Cookies and Technology&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;We use cookies only for functionality, such as keeping you logged in and remembering your preferences. We don&amp;rsquo;t use them for advertising or creepy tracking.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;You can manage cookies through your browser at any time.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Availability of Platform&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;We do our best to keep VoteYour running 24\/7, but we can&amp;rsquo;t guarantee there will be no interruptions or bugs. If maintenance or outages occur, we will aim to notify users as soon as possible.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Changes to the Platform or Terms&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;We may update these Terms occasionally. Major changes will be announced on the website or via email. Continuing to use the site means you accept any updated terms.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Termination&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/s